OL,3,EHEATHFIELDG````````````````````````````
OL,5,GThe Fat Sow is a nutter! To suggest    
OL,6,Gthat if you have the cash for a        
OL,7,GNintendo 64 but buy a PlayStation      
OL,8,Gbecause it's cheaper is akin to going  
OL,9,Gto a garage with the money to buy a    
OL,10,GFerrari and coming home in a Mini      
OL,11,GMetro. Not much fun.                   
OL,12,G                                       
OL,13,GIn this life you get what you pay for. 
OL,15,BAlex Sidorwicz, Stoke-on-Trent         
OL,17,FIt's just her opinion, man.            
