OL,3,ECHICHESTERG````````````````````````````
OL,5,GAfter denying the UK of quality like   
OL,6,GFinal Fantasy 3 and Mario RPG on SNES, 
OL,7,Git seems Nintendo are doing a repeat   
OL,8,Gwith N64. We have an inferior machine, 
OL,9,Gno effort's been made to counter a CPU 
OL,10,Gpower drain from the RF modulator, it's
OL,11,Ggames are costly and the machine's     
OL,12,Galready old hat in its home country.   
OL,14,GI suggest we ignore Nintendo until it  
OL,15,Goffers as good a service as Sega and,  
OL,16,Gin particular, Sony does in the UK.    
OL,17,BTim Carpenter                          
OL,19,FOn and on it goes...                   
