OL,3,EMIDHURSTG``````````````````````````````
OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,GIt's March 17 and I've still not bought
OL,6,GN64. I never will. Nintendo treats     
OL,7,GEurope like second class citizens.     
OL,9, We got poorer performance hardware,    
OL,10, months after its launch elsewhere, at  
OL,11, dearer prices. We also got a very weak 
OL,12, catalogue of games, with insane prices 
OL,13, and not much to look forward to in the 
OL,14, near/distant future.                   
OL,16,BGerry Ross                             
OL,18,FAnd on and on...                       
